metadata.name: Anesthasia.
metadata.description:
I'm cold

The weight of my eyelids overcomes my sanity
The weight of my members stops my walk
My breath doesn't feel like its own
I don't know if my heart belongs to me anymore

The haze of my memory distorts my face

"Sleep, it will all be over soon..."

Who accompanies me?
I'm not alone.
totally alone.

I'm scared but...
it does not hurt...
it doesn't hurt.
